OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772182876
OL,3,CPupils face three mile walk to school
OL,4,Cafter free school bus axed
OL,6,FDozens of parents with children at
OL,7,FHenry Beaufort School in Winchester
OL,8,Fhave protested outside the
OL,9,Fheadquarters of Hampshire County
OL,10,FCouncil as they call on politicians to
OL,11,Freverse a decision to axe a free
OL,12,Fschool bus.
OL,14,FFrom April the service from King's
OL,15,FWorthy to the 1,000 pupil secondary
OL,16,Fschool will stop. Families say it
OL,17,Fmeans some children will be forced to
OL,18,Fwalk three miles to school along a
OL,19,Froute they say is unsafe.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
