PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772182876
OL,3,CPupils face three mile walk to school
OL,4,Cafter free school bus axed
OL,6,FCampaigners are calling on Hampshire
OL,7,FCounty Council to rethink their
OL,8,Fdecision and made representations to a
OL,9,Fcouncil budget meeting as they lobbied
OL,10,Ffor a U-Turn.
OL,12,FOne parent, Danielle George, said: "At
OL,13,Fthe moment my options are to drive
OL,14,Fthem to and from school which is bad
OL,15,Ffor the environment, will impact my
OL,16,Fworking times and it's just not right.
OL,17,F"
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772182876
OL,3,CPupils face three mile walk to school
OL,4,Cafter free school bus axed
OL,6,FShe said the bus was why she chose the
OL,7,Fcatchment school because she knew her
OL,8,Fchildren could get to school safely.
OL,9,F"There is no public bus they can use
OL,10,Fas an alternative."
OL,12,FAnother mother said: "It's not a safe
OL,13,Fwalking route,. They would actually
OL,14,Fhave to cross over the A34 which is an
OL,15,Funlit crossing with cars going in
OL,16,Fexcess of 50 miles per hour."
OL,18,FPupils are also worried and turned out
OL,19,Ftoday (Thursday 26 February) to make
OL,20,Ftheir feelings known.
OL,26,@rD@SO]tD@VOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
