PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772182876
OL,3,CPupils face three mile walk to school
OL,4,Cafter free school bus axed
OL,6,F12-year-old Poppy said: "I'm not a
OL,7,Flazy person - I'd be fine walking if
OL,8,Fit was through a cul-de-sac but it's
OL,9,Fnot - it's through muddy fields. I
OL,10,Ffeel quite scared by it."
OL,12,FNoah, aged 13 , added: "I'm pretty
OL,13,Fannoyed about it. I'll have to stop
OL,14,Fclubs, I won't be able to hang out
OL,15,Fwith my friends after school and I'll
OL,16,Fhave less time to do homework and
OL,17,Fsocialise."
OL,26,@nD@YOUrD@YO]tD@XOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
