PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772182876
OL,3,CPupils face three mile walk to school
OL,4,Cafter free school bus axed
OL,6,FBut the worries go much wider. Local
OL,7,Fcouncillor Jackie Porter (LibDem) who
OL,8,Fis backing the parents said there are
OL,9,Fconcerns it might deter parents in the
OL,10,Ffuture from wanting their children to
OL,11,Fattend the schoo.
OL,13,F"We are concerned that parents will
OL,14,Fstop choosing Henry Beaufort beacuse
OL,15,Fit's a bad way of getting to school.
OL,16,FIt's a really fantastic school with a
OL,17,Frich and varied curriculum. It's
OL,18,Freally diverse and we don't want to
OL,19,Flose that from the Worthies."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
