PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772182876
OL,3,CPupils face three mile walk to school
OL,4,Cafter free school bus axed
OL,6,FA Hampshire County Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "National
OL,8,Flegislation makes free School
OL,9,FTransport available for secondary
OL,10,Fschool pupils where their walking
OL,11,Fdistance to school is more than three
OL,12,Fmiles. This is reduced to two miles
OL,13,Ffor students from low-income families.
OL,15,F"Following new housing development, a
OL,16,Fnew designated walking route has been
OL,17,Festablished between Kings Worthy and
OL,18,FHenry Beaufort, which is now under
OL,19,Fthree miles for most addresses in
OL,20,FKings Worthy.
OL,26,@oD@TOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
