OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772182876
OL,3,CPupils face three mile walk to school
OL,4,Cafter free school bus axed
OL,6,F"The route has been reviewed by a road
OL,7,Fsafety engineer in line with national
OL,8,Fguidance and assessed as available to
OL,9,Fwalk for secondary school age pupils,
OL,10,Faccompanied as appropriate. This
OL,11,Fchange means that from 13 April 2026,
OL,12,Fin line with all other available
OL,13,Fwalking routes that are under three
OL,14,Fmiles long in Hampshire and
OL,15,Fnationally, pupils living within this
OL,16,Fdistance will no longer be entitled to
OL,17,Ffree School Transport.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
