OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772182876
OL,3,CPupils face three mile walk to school
OL,4,Cafter free school bus axed
OL,6,F"This does not mean children have to
OL,7,Fwalk, that is at the discretion of
OL,8,Ftheir parents. Free transport will
OL,9,Fcontinue to be provided to any child
OL,10,Fwho needs to walk more than three
OL,11,Fmiles or who meets the criteria for
OL,12,Ffree transport due to SEN or income-
OL,13,Fbased eligibility."
OL,15,FAfter making their deputation parents
OL,16,Fwill now have to wait to see if
OL,17,Fcounclllors will change their minds.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
